flowchart TD
    A[Scan Directory] --> B[Find Diagram Files]
    B --> C{Manifest Exists?}
    C -->|No| D[Render All]
    C -->|Yes| E[Read Manifest]
    E --> F{For Each File}
    F --> G{Hash Changed?}
    G -->|Yes| D
    G -->|No| H{Theme Changed?}
    H -->|Yes| D
    H -->|No| I{Outputs Missing?}
    I -->|Yes| D
    I -->|No| J[Skip - Up to Date]
    D --> K[Render SVG]
    K --> L{Raster Formats?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Convert via sharp]
    L -->|No| N[Write Outputs]
    M --> N
    N --> O[Update Manifest<br/>hash + formats + outputs]
    O --> P[Clean Orphans]
    J --> P
